CodeAstra ~ The Code Editor

How to run the project:
- clone the project: ``git clone https://github.com/sandbox-science/CodeAstra.git``
- In the root directory, install the app: ``make``
- ``./build/CodeAstra`` to run the editor.

Disclammer:
This project has been tested on MacOS, but not yet on Windows nor Linux. Although, it should run on Linux without problem, but on Windows, you may encouter errors.

